<P><HI>Eleventhly,</HI> That the Governours of the
<HI>Ble$ Coa$ Ho&s;pital</HI> &s;hould undertake on the
Pa$ment to them of a rea&s;onable Sum
of Money by the City, to provide Main|tenance
for all &s;uch Children as the Ci|ty
&s;hould recommend to them; and to
