that is, at St. <HI>Giles</HI>'s near <HI>Long-Acre,</HI>
and about the North End o$ <HI>Drury-Lane;</HI>
al&s;o it &s;pread down <HI>Drury Lane into</HI>
St. <HI>Clements</HI> Pari&s;h, and the other way
