</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Brother.</SPEAKER>
<P>Ay, ju&s;t as I have done, <HI>Si&s;ter!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Si&s;ter.</SPEAKER>
<P>No, no, not as you have done,
