</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Brother.</SPEAKER>
<P>The thing is mo&s;t apt to the
Purpo&s;e, <HI>&s;earch and try our ways,</HI> which, as
I under&s;tand it is &s;elf Examination in the
$word$ Extreme.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Si&s;ter.</SPEAKER>
<P>Searching; that is, a looking back
upon our pa&s;t Life, and into every Acti|on
<PB N="214" REF="225">
of it; not hiding or dropping this
Search in any particular part that can
be brought to Memory; not covering any
