</LIST>
<P>On the contrary, in the three Weeks
above nam'd, the Numbers Bury'd within
the Walls of the City were as follow,
<LIST>
<LABEL>From the 29th of <HI>Augu&s;t,</HI> to the 5th
of <HI>September</HI></LABEL>
<ITEM>1118</ITEM>
